Winter is here, darkness descends … phones are taken, doors are shut, curtains are drawn on this quaint private theatre screen somewhere in Wierda Valley, Johannesburg. The preview small talk is unceremoniously drowned out by the hefty Dolby surround sound system. We know it is time when the bass is interrupted by an ominous and jarring silence. We sit still.
 
